<br>
I'll definitely look for some higher AC/hitpoint gear.  I'm guessing I should switch out my Ulthork Tunic for something that doesn't drop my hitpoints...  *giggle*  Bare minimum, I still have my old BCP in the bank...  =)<br>
<br>
Thanks, all!<br>
